Groupon says all current vouchers bought, will remain valid until the date stated on the purchase. JOHANNESBURG Groupon has shut down its operations in South Africa. The website that offered discounted deals since 2010, announced that it s winding down its operations in South Africa and will stop offering deals from tonight. Groupon however says all current vouchers bought, will remain valid until the date stated on the purchase. Customers uncomfortable with using the vouchers, can also get a cash voucher.(Edited by Leeto M Khoza)